##Bug Title
Secure Login Option Has No Action

##Description
After clicking on the Secure Login option, no action is performed and nothing happens.

##Steps to Reproduce
1. Open the application.
2. Enter a valid username and password.
3. Log in to the system.
4. Navigate to the Profile page.
5. Click on the Secure Login option.

##Expected Result
The user should be able to view the available secure login options and select one of them.

##Actual Result
After clicking on the Secure Login option, no action is performed and nothing happens.

##Severity
Medium

##Priority
Normal

##Test Environment
Browser: Chrome & Firefox
Operating System: win 11 & Android
